Description:
    Generates a screen with one basic grid.

Example:
    rails generate wulin_master:screen_and_grid Wulin name:string age:integer

    This will create:
        create  db/migrate/20110919093453_create_wulins.rb
        create  app/<asset_folder_name>/controllers/wulins_controller.rb
        create  app/<asset_folder_name>/screens/wulin_screen.rb
        create  app/<asset_folder_name>/grids/wulin_grid.rb
        create  app/<asset_folder_name>/models/wulin.rb
        create  app/<asset_folder_name>/views/wulins
        route  resources :wulins
        
    More info please run "rails generate wulin_master:screen_and_grid --help"  
        
        